entries.journal_entry_description: To ensure that the Empire doesn't get a foothold in the Corellia system, from where they can launch reinforcements and attacks on Restuss, you've been tasked with destroying any presence of military craft there.
entries.task00_journal_entry_description: The Alliance has tasked you with crippling the Imperial fleet in the Corellia system by destroying any 30 Imperial military craft there that you can find.
entries.task01_journal_entry_description: You have destroyed enough enemy fighters in the Corellia system and should return to Lieutenant Grollo in Restuss.
